OL,7,FSue Carter's world was shattered when
OL,8,Fher 25-year-old son Ryan died suddenly
OL,9,Ffollowing a cardiac arrest.
OL,11,FWhen Sue found out that there was a
OL,12,Fcharity that offered potentially life-
OL,13,Fsaving heart screening for young
OL,14,Fpeople - she dedicated herself to
OL,15,Fraising money.
OL,17,FSue runs craft events near her home in
OL,18,FTotton.
