OL,7,FSue's events have so far raised more
OL,8,Fthan #20,000, which has been used to
OL,9,Forganise the screening events.
OL,11,FSue's son Ryan was only 25 when he
OL,12,Fdied unexpectedly in 2019.
OL,14,F"He'd just basically had lunch, went
OL,15,Fupstairs, sat on the bed, and his
OL,16,Fgirlfriend went to the toilet, come
OL,17,Fback out, and he was gone," Sue said.
OL,19,F"But the post-mortem showed that his
OL,20,Fbody was fit and healthy, like he's
OL,21,Fjust gone to sleep.
