OL,7,F"More than 100 young people were
OL,8,Ftested at that event, she has another
OL,9,Fevent booked, so Sue is already on
OL,10,Fthat pathway to be saving young lives
OL,11,Fof other young people in a way
OL,12,Ftragically Ryan didn't have that
OL,13,Fopportunity."
OL,15,F"If Ryan knew you could be heart
OL,16,Fscreened beforehand, I know he would
OL,17,Fhave done that...because they are fit
OL,18,Fand healthy youngsters, the awareness
OL,19,Fisn't out there," Sue added.
